        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>The Ridge, Hartfield, | Tonbridge Wells</placeName>
                    <date>July 12<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>My dear Falconer</p>
<p>I thank you for your <hi rend="underline">most</hi> interesting note.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> The facts are really grand. We have had a melancholy household for some time; as my eldest girl has been very ill for a long time and we have brought her here for a change.<ref target="#foot.f3"/> I have been bad enough of late, and have not been in London for an age. Whenever I do come I must pay you a visit and have one of those chats with you, which I so much enjoy. But our plans are all uncertain being dependent on my daughter’s health.</p>
<p>I must say I do heartily enjoy Owen having had a good setting down—his arrogance and malignity are too bad.</p>
<p>My good old friend | Yours most truly | C. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        

        

