            <note xml:id="foot.f3">The Darwins had taken <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1225.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Henrietta Emma Darwin</ref> to convalesce at the home of Sarah Elizabeth Wedgwood in Hartfield, Sussex (‘Journal’; Appendix II).</note>
